--Screenshot_2025-03-12_at_4.52.49_PM.png 2x\"/\u003e\u003csource srcset=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" media=\"(min-width: 768px)\" data-srcset=\"https://images.food52.com/hHNwQafYTBrrngzdVR0ina_zIho=/964x1191/6d16c1ea-9056-4c71-9f8f-8204fa0c38ce--Screenshot_2025-03-12_at_4.52.49_PM.png, https://images.food52.com/BjTJBaYgJDD1VWqOCsDK_6WeyiM=/1928x2382/6d16c1ea-9056-4c71-9f8f-8204fa0c38ce--Screenshot_2025-03-12_at_4.52.49_PM.png 2x\"/\u003e\u003csource srcset=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" media=\"(min-width: 500px)\" type=\"image/webp\" data-srcset=\"https://images.food52.com/c8DE0BtJTVLs8cuKZOYIsg0W0qE=/768x949/filters:format(webp)/6d16c1ea-9056-4c71-9f8f-8204fa0c38ce--Screenshot_2025-03-12_at_4.52.49_PM.png, https://images.food52.com/uXBTutdQElNIDMefuV2zFnBoUj4=/1536x1898/filters:format(webp)/6d16c1ea-9056-4c71-9f8f-8204fa0c38ce--Screenshot_2025-03-12_at_4.52.49_PM.png 2x\"/\u003e\u003csource srcset=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" media=\"(min-width: 500px)\" data-srcset=\"https://images.food52.com/6m0GBSHQWsXnt6cLO7EOZgiCKq0=/768x949/6d16c1ea-9056-4c71-9f8f-8204fa0c38ce--Screenshot_2025-03-12_at_4.52.49_PM.png, https://images.food52.com/bcoM1JJv4L-aMzmYLVKrdJJaLyE=/1536x1898/6d16c1ea-9056-4c71-9f8f-8204fa0c38ce--Screenshot_2025-03-12_at_4.52.49_PM.png 2x\"/\u003e\u003csource srcset=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" type=\"image/webp\" data-srcset=\"https://images.food52.com/jUyyj-HFO_9XGFNZcg9VeWGbFtU=/375x463/filters:format(webp)/6d16c1ea-9056-4c71-9f8f-8204fa0c38ce--Screenshot_2025-03-12_at_4.52.49_PM.png, https://images.food52.com/MWowzHtmJrY1It8g8XyvR9X9fqQ=/750x926/filters:format(webp)/6d16c1ea-9056-4c71-9f8f-8204fa0c38ce--Screenshot_2025-03-12_at_4.52.49_PM.png 2x\"/\u003e\u003cimg srcset=\"https://images.food52.com/XtHAN-H3wWtZWafz8OI7Q752NJM=/375x463/6d16c1ea-9056-4c71-9f8f-8204fa0c38ce--Screenshot_2025-03-12_at_4.52.49_PM.png, https://images.food52.com/o2_siOYU-3FYI-KOOrU6dlqIlHU=/750x926/6d16c1ea-9056-4c71-9f8f-8204fa0c38ce--Screenshot_2025-03-12_at_4.52.49_PM.png 2x\" alt=\"Unbaked onion \u0026#34;chips.\u0026#34;\" width=\"964\" height=\"1191\" data-expand=\"750\" data-srcset=\"https://images.food52.com/XtHAN-H3wWtZWafz8OI7Q752NJM=/375x463/6d16c1ea-9056-4c71-9f8f-8204fa0c38ce--Screenshot_2025-03-12_at_4.52.49_PM.png, https://images.food52.com/o2_siOYU-3FYI-KOOrU6dlqIlHU=/750x926/6d16c1ea-9056-4c71-9f8f-8204fa0c38ce--Screenshot_2025-03-12_at_4.52.49_PM.png 2x\"/\u003e\u003c/picture\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n    \u003c/div\u003e\n\n      \u003cfigcaption\u003e\n          \u003cspan\u003eUnbaked onion \u0026#34;chips.\u0026#34;\u003c/span\u003e\n\n          \u003cspan\u003ePhoto by Anna Arriaga\u003c/span\u003e\n      \u003c/figcaption\u003e\n  \u003c/figure\u003e\n\n              \u003cp\u003eFirst, I preheat the oven to 400 degrees fahrenheit and lay out parchment paper onto a big baking sheet. Next, I spread shredded parmesan cheese all over the baking sheet until it created a thin, even layer of cheese over the whole baking sheet. You can measure with your heart here, because the cheese is what makes the chips so deliciously crispy. Then, I cut my onions into uniform, thin slices until I had enough to cover the baking sheet fully with onion slices laying flat. The creator of this recipe, \u003ca href=\"https://hungryhappens.net/2-ingredient-onion-ring-chips-low-carb/\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eStella Drivas\u003c/a\u003e, uses a mandoline to ensure those thin, uniform slices. After laying those onion slices flat over the cheese layer, I brushed the onions with some olive oil, garlic powder, paprika, and salt. You can add or subtract any seasonings to this part.\u003c/p\u003e\n              \u003cp\u003eThen, I put that baking sheet to bake for about 18 minutes until it looked just crispy enough without being burnt and let it all cool for a few minutes. If you don’t let it rest, the cheese won\u0026#39;t get as crispy!\u003c/p\u003e\n              \n\n\n  \n\n              \n\n  \u003cfigure\u003e\n    \u003cdiv\u003e\n      \u003ca href=\"https://www.pinterest.com/pin/create/button\" data-pin-do=\"buttonPin\" data-pin-media=\"\" data-pin-description=\"One onion chip.\" data-pin-custom=\"true\" data-ga-event=\"inPageInteraction\" data-ga-event-action=\"Pinterest Share\" data-ga-event-label=\"Article Body Image\" data-ga-destination-url=\"none\"\u003e\n        \u003csvg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 16.9 20.8\"\u003e\u003cpath d=\"M16.8 6.3C16.5 3.2 13.6.4 10.1.1 4.8-.5.1 2.7 0 7.9c0 2.4.8 4 2.9 4.8 1.5-1.5-.3-2.4-.5-4C2 4.3 7.1.1 11.7 2.9c3.2 1.9 2.6 9.9-1.2 10.7-.8.1-1.8-.1-2.1-.5-1.9-1.8 1.5-4.8.4-7.3-.9-2.1-3.6-.4-3.9 1.5-.2 1 .3 2 .3 2.9 0 2.1-1.3 5-1.7 7.1-.2.9-.3 2.6-.1 3.4h1.5c1-1.6 1.6-4.1 2.1-6.3.3-.2.5.4.7.6 1.8 1.4 5 .6 6.4-.7 2.1-1.7 3-5.2 2.7-8\" fill=\"currentColor\"\u003e\u003c/path\u003e\u003c/svg\u003e\n      \u003c/a\u003e\n\n      \u003cdiv\u003e\u003cpicture\u003e\u003csource srcset=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" media=\"(min-width: 1400px)\" type=\"image/webp\" data-srcset=\"https://images.food52.com/OEiLcn--1AK9yPzG2wcsjgBLIGQ=/778x1000/filters:format(webp)/38e55afe-d1a6-4bf1-8602-e03868ccc109--Screenshot_2025-03-12_at_4.58.25_PM.png, https://images.food52.com/hoNchkSmQa1IIMUfKUazDUqp3s0=/1556x2000/filters:format(webp)/38e55afe-d1a6-4bf1-8602-e03868ccc109--Screenshot_2025-03-12_at_4.58.25_PM.png 2x\"/\u003e\u003csource srcset=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" media=\"(min-width: 1400px)\" data-srcset=\"https://images.food52.com/TxvKqzkCUz5rdIgCzM-QHr3azvA=/778x1000/38e55afe-d1a6-4bf1-8602-e03868ccc109--Screenshot_2025-03-12_at_4.58.25_PM.png, https://images.food52.com/jZUFN9cA2QjjDP6bMVZTl5tzLfQ=/1556x2000/38e55afe-d1a6-4bf1-8602-e03868ccc109--Screenshot_2025-03-12_at_4.58.25_PM.png 2x\"/\u003e\u003csource srcset=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" media=\"(min-width: 1024px)\" type=\"image/webp\" data-srcset=\"https://images.food52.com/dA6UDGTrx4lf7uM5BxM4nMH4iDI=/660x848/filters:format(webp)/38e55afe-d1a6-4bf1-8602-e03868ccc109--Screenshot_2025-03-12_at_4.58.25_PM.png, https://images.food52.com/FOEZLiDBr2dOjOBIcNWfK4m3L6M=/1320x1696/filters:format(webp)/38e55afe-d1a6-4bf1-8602-e03868ccc109--Screenshot_2025-03-12_at_4.58.25_PM.png 2x\"/\u003e\u003csource srcset=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" media=\"(min-width: 1024px)\" data-srcset=\"https://images.food52.com/GqhbZywnkiNkmEZegAWF_WqNVEU=/660x848/38e55afe-d1a6-4bf1-8602-e03868ccc109--Screenshot_2025-03-12_at_4.58.25_PM.png, https://images.food52.com/8kP3cA0kQ17uer3UyMEbLA7r5jg=/1320x1696/38e55afe-d1a6-4bf1-8602-e03868ccc109--Screenshot_2025-03-12_at_4.58.25_PM.png 2x\"/\u003e\u003csource srcset=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" media=\"(min-width: 768px)\" type=\"image/webp\" data-srcset=\"https://images.food52.com/rJHnfXNDd68ro1MK58dVzEMToS4=/964x1239/filters:format(webp)/38e55afe-d1a6-4bf1-8602-e03868ccc109--Screenshot_2025-03-12_at_4.58.25_PM.png, https://images.food52.com/GZrgVSGpOHfY4hF3wAl2qRBkvwk=/1928x2478/filters:format(webp)/38e55afe-d1a6-4bf1-8602-e03868ccc109--Screenshot_2025-03-12_at_4.58.25_PM.png 2x\"/\u003e\u003csource srcset=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" media=\"(min-width: 768px)\" data-srcset=\"https://images.food52.com/y4_EeAr7noy1NW5Ke2ouu24U4Wc=/964x1239/38e55afe-d1a6-4bf1-8602-e03868ccc109--Screenshot_2025-03-12_at_4.58.25_PM.png, https://images.food52.com/2KpedGSnmI7gwySWc-Qn1NKu7gM=/1928x2478/38e55afe-d1a6-4bf1-8602-e03868ccc109--Screenshot_2025-03-12_at_4.58.25_PM.png 2x\"/\u003e\u003csource srcset=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" media=\"(min-width: 500px)\" type=\"image/webp\" data-srcset=\"https://images.food52.com/X-KVumQBgKL69PFVTOEpsSah9KI=/768x987/filters:format(webp)/38e55afe-d1a6-4bf1-8602-e03868ccc109--Screenshot_2025-03-12_at_4.58.25_PM.png, https://images.food52.com/v0alSy9ku-kWrSEm3VIc_ng-Q7g=/1536x1974/filters:format(webp)/38e55afe-d1a6-4bf1-8602-e03868ccc109--Screenshot_2025-03-12_at_4.58.25_PM.png 2x\"/\u003e\u003csource srcset=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" media=\"(min-width: 500px)\" data-srcset=\"https://images.food52.com/tYdkJY1u4sai5dmnvN1kiTMtoK4=/768x987/38e55afe-d1a6-4bf1-8602-e03868ccc109--Screenshot_2025-03-12_at_4.58.25_PM.png, https://images.food52.com/uQuhDf6OeoobslzfKqQPCV5HIk8=/1536x1974/38e55afe-d1a6-4bf1-8602-e03868ccc109--Screenshot_2025-03-12_at_4.58.25_PM.png 2x\"/\u003e\u003csource srcset=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" type=\"image/webp\" data-srcset=\"https://images.food52.com/k9BCaTZ9UBYYpJ7uTQmrdkKpgKw=/375x482/filters:format(webp)/38e55afe-d1a6-4bf1-8602-e03868ccc109--Screenshot_2025-03-12_at_4.58.25_PM.png, https://images.food52.com/GJn7ItuSKx86NfohDH-8B3b4PVk=/750x964/filters:format(webp)/38e55afe-d1a6-4bf1-8602-e03868ccc109--Screenshot_2025-03-12_at_4.58.25_PM.png 2x\"/\u003e\u003cimg srcset=\"https://images.food52.com/OFseF8jX9KfeUIWw_kW6fiGsIHQ=/375x482/38e55afe-d1a6-4bf1-8602-e03868ccc109--Screenshot_2025-03-12_at_4.58.25_PM.png, https://images.food52.com/Kedhie1Zoj0jMWHG5tk6wBgSXv4=/750x964/38e55afe-d1a6-4bf1-8602-e03868ccc109--Screenshot_2025-03-12_at_4.58.25_PM.png 2x\" alt=\"One onion chip.\" width=\"964\" height=\"1239\" data-expand=\"750\" data-srcset=\"https://images.food52.com/OFseF8jX9KfeUIWw_kW6fiGsIHQ=/375x482/38e55afe-d1a6-4bf1-8602-e03868ccc109--Screenshot_2025-03-12_at_4.58.25_PM.png, https://images.food52.com/Kedhie1Zoj0jMWHG5tk6wBgSXv4=/750x964/38e55afe-d1a6-4bf1-8602-e03868ccc109--Screenshot_2025-03-12_at_4.58.25_PM.png 2x\"/\u003e\u003c/picture\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n    \u003c/div\u003e\n\n      \u003cfigcaption\u003e\n          \u003cspan\u003eOne onion chip.\u003c/span\u003e\n\n          \u003cspan\u003ePhoto by Anna Arriaga\u003c/span\u003e\n      \u003c/figcaption\u003e\n  \u003c/figure\u003e\n\n              \u003cp\u003eThese chips were seriously good. While they’re not exactly as fluffy and tasty as a breaded onion ring, it’s a fun snack to meal prep for the week or to prepare if you’re having people over in a pinch. It also made the test kitchen smell \u003cem\u003eheavenly,\u003c/em\u003e like french fries without the hassle of a deep fryer.\u003c/p\u003e\n              \u003cp\u003eNext time, I think I’d experiment with the different seasonings and maybe make an accompanying dipping sauce. The possibilities are endless: onion chip nachos, onion chip towers, or even onion chips layered in a sandwich.\u003c/p\u003e\n              \u003chr/\u003e\n\n              \u003cp\u003e\u003cem\u003eWhat other trending recipes do you want to know more about? Let me know below!\u003c/em\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n          \u003c/div\u003e\n      \u003c/div\u003e\n\n  \n  \u003cdiv\u003e\n      \u003ch3\u003ePopular on Food52\u003c/h3\u003e\n      \n    \u003c/div\u003e\n\n  \n\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e",
